The <strong><code>display</code></strong> <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS">CSS</a> property sets whether an element is treated as a <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flow_Layout" rel="nofollow">block or inline element</a> and the layout used for its children, such as <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Grid_Layout" rel="nofollow">grid</a> or <a href="/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Flexible_Box_Layout" rel="nofollow">flex</a>.